          <li>Finical 3D is not liable for any indirect, consequential, special, or incidental loss or damage, including loss of profit, loss of business, or damage to reputation, even if advised of the possibility of such loss.</li>
          <li>Finical 3D is not liable for any loss or damage arising from the Client's use or misuse of printed parts, including use in applications for which the material or design is unsuitable.</li>
          <li>Our liability is not excluded or limited in relation to death or personal injury caused by our negligence, or for fraudulent misrepresentation.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <hr class="terms-divider">

      <!-- 15 -->
      <section class="terms-section" id="s15">
        <span class="section-number">15</span>
        <h2>Consumer Guarantees Act &amp; Fair Trading Act</h2>
        <p>Where you are a <strong>consumer</strong> as defined by the New Zealand Consumer Guarantees Act 1993 (CGA), you have statutory rights that cannot be excluded by these Terms, including guarantees that services will be carried out with reasonable care and skill and that goods will be of acceptable quality.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Where the CGA applies, nothing in these Terms overrides your statutory rights.</li>
          <li>If you are acquiring our services for the purpose of a business, you agree that the CGA does not apply to that supply, and our liability is governed by these Terms.</li>
          <li>Finical 3D complies with the Fair Trading Act 1986 and does not engage in misleading or deceptive conduct.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <hr class="terms-divider">

      <!-- 16 -->
      <section class="terms-section" id="s16">
        <span class="section-number">16</span>
        <h2>Privacy</h2>
        <p>Finical 3D collects and holds personal information (name, contact details, order history) for the purpose of providing services, invoicing, and communicating with you.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>We comply with the New Zealand Privacy Act 2020.</li>
          <li>Your information will not be sold or disclosed to third parties except as required to fulfil your order (e.g. courier services) or as required by law.</li>
          <li>You have the right to request access to and correction of personal information held about you. Requests can be directed to <a href="mailto:matt@finical3d.co.nz">matt@finical3d.co.nz</a>.</li>
          <li>Design files submitted by Clients are treated as confidential and will not be shared without consent. See Section 6 for file retention details.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <hr class="terms-divider">

      <!-- 17 -->
      <section class="terms-section" id="s17">
        <span class="section-number">17</span>
        <h2>Governing Law &amp; Disputes</h2>
        <p>These Terms are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of <strong>New Zealand</strong>. Any dispute arising under these Terms will be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the New Zealand courts.</p>
        <p>Before initiating formal proceedings, both parties agree to attempt to resolve any dispute in good faith through direct communication. If a resolution cannot be reached, either party may refer the matter to the Disputes Tribunal (for claims up to $30,000) or such other dispute resolution body as may be appropriate.</p>
      </section>
      <hr class="terms-divider">

      <!-- 18 -->
      <section class="terms-section" id="s18">
        <span class="section-number">18</span>
        <h2>Changes to These Terms</h2>
        <p>Finical 3D reserves the right to update or amend these Terms at any time. The current version will always be published on our website with an updated effective date. Continued use of our services following a change constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms.</p>
        <p>For ongoing or multi-stage projects, the Terms in effect at the time of the original order confirmation will apply unless otherwise agreed.</p>
      </section>
      <hr class="terms-divider">

      <!-- 19 -->
      <section class="terms-section" id="s19">
        <span class="section-number">19</span>
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about these Terms, or wish to discuss an order, please get in touch:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Business:</strong> Finical 3D</li>
          <li><strong>Location:</strong> Christchurch, Canterbury, New Zealand</li>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:matt@finical3d.co.nz">matt@finical3d.co.nz</a></li>
          <li><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:+64211752398">+64 21 175 2398</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- Contact strip -->
